   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-c" mid="118" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="117"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9871_qu_01.ogg}<BR>...I was thinking about how to bring it up.<BR>Your glass is empty. I'll fill it for you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-d" mid="120" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="119"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Hm.<BR>Knowing you, you've already planned everything before calling me. Did something suddenly change?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-e" mid="122" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="121"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Fine. I'll tell you the truth. Actually, I….<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(You hear the sound of uneven footsteps before Vernicka can explain.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2" mid="124" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="123"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Should I give you some space?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-" mid="183" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="125"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>……No, there's no need. You can listen in.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-a" mid="127" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="126"><![CDATA[<html>$Mystical Girl${sound:npc_Kali_qu9871_sp_01.ogg}<BR>I have returned with a letter from Norfe.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-b" mid="129" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="128"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I didn't expect it so quickly.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-c" mid="131" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="130"><![CDATA[<html>$Mystical Girl$<BR>As I am not from Mistland, you won't listen no matter what I say.<BR>I'll read you the interesting part.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-c" image="QN_Hologram.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-d" mid="133" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="132"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe's Letter$<BR><FONT color=#086171>……"Dear President Vernicka: although your plan was meticulously devised, you can see the tragic results for yourself. Due to your botch up, the Anti-Goddess Faction almost lost Grele, our most precious asset. But we're not the only ones who would suffer from this incident."</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-d" image="QN_Hologram.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-e" mid="135" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="134"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe's Letter$<BR><FONT color=#086171>"President Vernicka, you have made the mistake of breaking the balance of power that was precariously in check. More importantly, you've lost our trust. Merca is a city that thrives on the conflict between the Goddess Followers and the Anti-Goddess Faction so I'm sure you know very well how losing our trust would affect your city in the long run.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-e" image="QN_Hologram.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-f" mid="137" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="136"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe's Letter$<BR><FONT color=#086171>"Merca will also be in a dire situation in the near future. Child Mamon is absorbing Grele's jewel right now so she is not taking any action, but where would she attack next when she recovers?"<BR>"Merca's Heart is a strategic location with mines full of Goldstones. Your city will be her next target."</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-f" image="QN_Hologram.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-g" mid="139" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="138"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe's Letter$<BR><FONT color=#086171>"The Anti-Goddess Faction in the Southern Lands is closest to Mamon's territory and it's us who can find out about her activities more quickly than anyone else."<BR>..."If you're not thinking of turning away from the Anti-Goddess Faction for good, I hope you can make the right decision this time."</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-h" mid="141" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="140"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(After listening to Norfe's letter, Vernicka turns pale.)</FONT><BR>...He's right, dammit.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-i" mid="143" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="142"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I acknowledge it. I didn't realize it would come to this.<BR>Go and tell Norfe that I admit all my mistakes and would like to send my apologies.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-j" mid="145" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="144"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>We will support you with money, men, ...whatever you need to treat Grele. I will send my soldiers too if the Anti-Goddess Faction needs them.<BR>I promise my full support for the Anti-Goddess Faction for it to regain stability.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-k" mid="147" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="146"><![CDATA[<html>$Mystical Girl${sound:npc_Kali_qu9871_sp_02.ogg}<BR>You only become cooperative when you fear Merca is in immediate danger.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-l" mid="149" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="148"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9871_qu_02.ogg}<BR>Everyone has a different perspective on what is important.<BR>...Merca's Heart is everything to me.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-m" mid="151" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="150"><![CDATA[<html>$Mystical Girl${sound:npc_Kali_qu9871_sp_03.ogg}<BR>Okay, I'll convey your message to Norfe. One last thing...<BR>What you told Grele about Hiver's relics... Was that all a lie, too?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-n" mid="153" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="152"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>It's true that relics were discovered. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka sighs.)</FONT><BR>Grele seems to have left the relics. I'll collect them later and send them to Rhadames.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-o" mid="155" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="154"><![CDATA[<html>$Mystical Girl${sound:npc_Kali_qu9871_sp_04.ogg}<BR>… Vernicka, even after all this, I still want to be able to trust you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-2-p" mid="157" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="156"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>That's very fortunate...<BR>I can't help it if you don't trust me, but I do value my relationship with you, and I would be sorry if it ended here.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2937_kali-2-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2937_kali-3" mid="159" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="158"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka closes his eyes as if he doesn't want to talk any more, looking distressed for the first time.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
